fields.label: Invoice Number
fields.description: If adding a new invoice, then make the Invoice Number the same value as Reference ID. If updating an existing invoice, then make it the same value as the Reference ID of that invoice. If you do not make the Invoice Number the same as Reference ID, then duplicate Invoice Numbers for different invoices may be created. The Reference ID is the only value checked as a unique identifier. Note that the name of the Reference ID is different for each invoice type: e.g. Supplier Invoice ID, Supplier Invoice Adjustment ID, Customer Invoice Adjustment ID, and Customer Invoice ID.
